headline: LKQ Corporation (LKQ) Fell Due to Lackluster Performance
summary: Scout Investments, Inc., an affiliate of Carillon Tower Advisers, released the “Carillon Scout Mid Cap Fund” second quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The Russell Midcap Index posted positive returns in the second quarter despite a sharp sell-off at the beginning of April following the liberation Day tariff announcement. […]
